step_data.thought: I've filled in the 'Category Name' field with 'Electronics'. Now I need to save this new product category to complete the creation process. Looking at the page, I can see a 'Save' button with ID 838 at the top of the form. Clicking this button will save the new Electronics category as a subcategory under the main category (ID: 2).
